155
00:19:08,633 --> 00:19:11,802
Odvalices glavu
staroj sa tom motkom?

156
00:19:28,569 --> 00:19:29,946
Spavaj ove noci
sa Simonom.

157
00:19:30,780 --> 00:19:34,200
