ces umreti?

171
00:21:40,535 --> 00:21:42,870
Ali dobro...
Kakvo je to pitanje?

172
00:21:43,955 --> 00:21:46,165
Pa, umrecu
kroz mnogo, mnogo,

173
00:21:46,290 --> 00:21:47,333
